metadata.name: Nil Sine Numini
metadata.description:
Nil Sine Numini is a mixed media on wooden board digitalized in jpeg 4550 x 4538px



Nil Sine Numini is a latin proverb meaning
nothing without the divine will


it was entirely hand painted , as i ve been a real art world artist for the past 25 years, my adventure in web3 has showed me new paths 

“Life isn't about finding yourself. Life is about creating yourself.”
― George Bernard Shaw
